    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "I'm so excited for the Open Campus!",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "MotionName": "w-cute02-glad",
          "FacialName": "face_smile_02",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_02_02_20",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 1,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "(When I was looking up fashion schools, I thought this one seemed really nice.)",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 2,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "MotionName": "w-cool10-tilthead",
          "FacialName": "face_smile_01",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_02_03_20",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "(Since they have a lot of different courses, you can study exactly what you want to learn in depth—)",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 2,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "MotionName": "w-normal15-tilthead",
          "FacialName": "face_smile_01",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_02_04_20",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "(They have internships with fashion companies, and famous designers as instructors... And quite a few current students have even won awards in contests, right?)",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 2,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "MotionName": "w-normal15-shy",
          "FacialName": "face_smile_01",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_02_05_20",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "(Looks like they'll be on display at today's Open Campus, too... I can't wait to see what kind of pieces they have!)",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 2,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "MotionName": "w-cute01-tilthead",
          "FacialName": "face_smile_01",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_02_06_20",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "???",
      "Body": "'—Mizuki.'",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_02_07_21_night",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "Huh?",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "MotionName": "w-normal01-tiltheadB",
          "FacialName": "face_smallmouth_01",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_02_08_20",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 1,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "Ah, Miku! What's up?",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "MotionName": "w-cute01-forward03",
          "FacialName": "face_notice_01",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_02_09_20",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 303
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Miku",
      "Body": "'I heard you were making an amazing MV, so I came to see.'",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 303,
          "MotionName": "w-normal15-tilthead",
          "FacialName": "face_night_normal_01",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 303,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_02_10_21_night",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 1,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 303
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Miku",
      "Body": "'...You're outside?'",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 303,
          "MotionName": "w-normal15-tilthead",
          "FacialName": "face_night_smallmouth_01",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 303,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_02_11_21_night",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "Ah, sorry, even though you came all this way to see...! Today is the Open Campus for a school called Tokyo Fashion Design Academy!",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "MotionName": "w-normal03-blushed",
          "FacialName": "face_smile_06",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_02_12_20",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 303
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Miku",
      "Body": "'Open Campus...?'",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 303,
          "MotionName": "w-normal1503-tilthead",
          "FacialName": "face_night_smallmouth_01",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 303,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_02_13_21_night",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "Yep! It's a day where you can visit the school before enrolling to experience the classes and the overall atmosphere!",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "MotionName": "w-cute14-nod",
          "FacialName": "face_smile_01",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_02_14_20",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "The one I'm going to today is a fashion vocational school I've been interested in. They said you can see exhibits from current students and even a fashion show!",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "MotionName": "w-happy14-tilthead",
          "FacialName": "face_smile_01",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_02_15_20",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "Plus, there's a workshop where you can design your own clothes!",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "MotionName": "w-cool10-tilthead",
          "FacialName": "face_smile_01",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_02_16_20",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 303
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Miku",
      "Body": "'I see... It sounds like fun.'",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 303,
          "MotionName": "w-normal16-nod",
          "FacialName": "face_night_smallmouth_01",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 303,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_02_17_21_night",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "Right, right!? Oh, if you'd like, do you want to look around with me, Miku?",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "MotionName": "w-cute02-glad",
          "FacialName": "face_smile_02",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_02_18_20",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 303
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Miku",
      "Body": "'Is that okay?'",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 303,
          "MotionName": "w-normal1607-tilthead",
          "FacialName": "face_night_smallmouth_01",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 303,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_02_19_21_night",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "Of course! I was planning on walking around by myself anyway.",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "MotionName": "w-happy02-nod",
          "FacialName": "face_smile_02",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_02_20_20",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "Ah, you'll have to watch secretly, though...",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "MotionName": "w-cool02-tilthead",
          "FacialName": "face_smile_06",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_02_21_20",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 303
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Miku",
      "Body": "'...Yeah, I'd like to see it with you.'",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 303,
          "MotionName": "w-normal03-nod",
          "FacialName": "face_night_smile_01",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 303,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_02_22_21_night",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 303
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Miku",
      "Body": "'Thank you, Mizuki.'",
